    {
      "scene_id": "scene_002",
      "scene_number": 2,
      "text": "INT. MR. PATEL'S APARTMENT - LIVING ROOM - LATER THAT AFTERNOON\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:03:30]\nChaos has begun. Folding tables crammed everywhere. Guests mill about in hoodies, sipping from red cups. A fluffy orange CAT (named \"Sir Whiskers\") prowls like he owns the place.\n\nJake and Mia set up frantically. Jake balances a tray of sliders while dodging elbows.\n\nGUEST #1 (excited tech bro)\nYo, these sliders look fire! What's the special sauce?\n\nJAKE\nUh... love? And aioli. Mostly aioli.\n\nSir Whiskers leaps onto the table, knocks over a bowl of dip. It splatters across three guests.\n\nGUEST #2\nMy new Yeezys!\n\nMIA\n(under her breath)\nGreat. Now we're catering a crime scene.\n\nJake tries to shoo the cat. Sir Whiskers hisses, swats the tray\u2014sliders fly like frisbees. One lands in a guest's drink. Another sticks to the ceiling fan, which starts spinning slowly, flinging sauce.\n\nGUESTS\n(laughing, some horrified)\nWhat the\u2014?!",
